properties.areaDesc: Melville Foothills; Southern Wheatland; Judith Gap
properties.headline: High Wind Warning issued January 30 at 2:21PM MST until February 2 at 6:00AM MST by NWS Billings MT
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds gusting up to 60 mph.

* WHERE...Judith Gap, Melville Foothills and Southern Wheatland.

* WHEN...From 6 AM Saturday to 6 AM MST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Strong crosswinds will make travel difficult along Highway
191 from Melville through Judith Gap. Damaging winds will blow
down trees and power lines.

* FIRE CONCERNS...High winds, unseasonably warm temperatures, and
low humidities will result in elevated grassland fire danger.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

Additional graphics for
this hazard can be found at http://www.weather.gov/billings

NWSheadline: HIGH WIND WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 6 AM SATURDAY TO 6 AM MST SUNDAY
